      "writtenOn": "2021-07-09T12:40:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Note: Swarming bots reboot both on a timer (at least every 24 hours) and whenever a task fails.  AFAIK they do not reboot after every task, so depending on how lazy the unmount is, it seems possible that a second task could start running before the ramdisk has been unmounted, which could lead to OOM or other issues.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 54,
        "startChar": 31,
        "endLine": 54,
        "endChar": 78
      },
      "revId": "8910b347a4fbb678eb9e4a050a9e444d6400c82c",
